data.description: Great equity builder with this spacious home featuring all living facilities on one level! Large main floor bedroom with 2 additional rooms in the lower level that need an egress window to be considered legal bedrooms. Updated bathroom on main floor with rough-in bath in LL would make this a 3 bed, 2 bath home! A generously sized kitchen, cozy gas fireplace, and a delightful three-season porch that leads to fenced yard with small pond, perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. Property includes an apple tree, along with blueberry and raspberry bushes. One-stall garage, a new roof installed in 2023, and stucco siding! Come check it out today!
